About Concrete

Parent for Concrete - Java libraries.

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Safe Library for use with Concrete that provides compile-time safety in order to defeat issues around 'requiredness' in Thrift.
Utility Utility library for use with Concrete-Java
Validation Validation library for use with Concrete-Java
Ingester Base Common library for Concrete document ingesters.
Simple Ingester Library containing simple Concrete document ingesters, not specific to any corpus.
